          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/55_step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a medium pot with a very generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the remaining <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until they're beginning to break down&nbsp;</p>",
